Maven dependency

<dependency>
  <groupId>com.azure</groupId>
  <artifactId>azure-messaging-servicebus</artifactId>
  <version>7.17.5</version> <!-- latest 7.x at time of writing -->
</dependency>

App Settings needed
	•	AzureWebJobsServiceBus (or your own name): Service Bus connection string with Send rights to the target queue.
	•	(Optionally) move notification-request queue name to an app setting and read via System.getenv("SB_NOTIFICATION_QUEUE").

That’s it—drop these in and call the 3-line send block after you build your JSON.